comments.body:
Potential more concise alternative (works for DisableCategory too):
```suggestion
    if (flag == BCLog::NONE) return;
    StdLockGuard scoped_lock(m_cs);
    flag == BCLog::ALL ? m_categories.set() : m_categories.set(flag);
```

